Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.33,0:22:45.41,Roman2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}oto wo nakushita shiroki karechi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.33,0:22:45.41,English2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Pour both abundance and color,
