Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.41,0:22:51.44,Roman2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}afureru iro wo sosoideku
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.41,0:22:51.44,English2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Unto this white, forsaken land which has lost its music.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.44,0:22:55.53,Moonspeak2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}あざやかに・・・
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.44,0:22:55.53,Roman2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}azayaka ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.44,0:22:55.53,English2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}They shall bring prosperity.
